darks.orm.annotation
注释类型 Temporary

@Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Temporary

Indicates the attribute of entity class is temporary to store some temporary datas in entity object. If the attribute use Temporary annotation, it will be filtered, when the entity object is persisted or updated.
